blog.name: pamela-poison
blog.title: Poison Ivy: The Origin Story
blog.description: Before she was the most desired Gotham City Siren, notorius Arkham resident, and independent non-counterpart in all of DC's comic women, she was Pam Isley. This page is one of many social profiles for the fan-fiction live action screenplay currently based out of Los Angeles, California.  In effort to fundraise the untold story of the most misunderstood and misinterpreted woman in all of Gotham, and to support starving film kids who dream of overturning the wreckage of modern comic lore in cinema, you can find our gofundme through our youtube channel. Copy and paste this link in your broswer to view the proposed trailer we made in two days with zero budget, and don't forget to subscribe! : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8iS1aUdS7jg

summary: I love how when Loki died in IW i was mad about it but now that they tease him coming back im just like "they cant let him stay...
body:
I love how when Loki died in IW i was mad about it but now that they tease him coming back im just like “they cant let him stay dead cant they”…

Like instead of these expected and tiring comebacks just….. not kill him in the first place yknow…..

If hes gonna come back every time he dies then just stop killing him its getting boring now, they wasted him in IW

Rather had him in all of IW then let him die in the end cus thats enough that I would need tbh

summary: Ant-Man & The Wasp Summary That May Not Make Sense
body:
Ant-Man & The Wasp Summary That May Not Make Sense

Basically there are a bunch of different people after Scott that you constantly forget exist because someone else is coming after him.

Like Jimmy Woo and the FBI keep breaking into his house, and then there is that guy Sunny who you literally don’t remember until he makes his way into the plot again not to forget our main girl Ghost who is actually just misunderstood and that Professor guy Goliath or whatever who changes heart.

Like there are so many teams of peopel and they just all come at my boy Scott😂
